{"tid":1741512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(無圖) 中國屋苑擁有全球最強人工湖","createTime":"2019-11-20T11:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T11:38:45.000Z","uid":101917,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"089aa991bab1041310eebf361f6d3665ffea5870","tid":1741512,"uid":101917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長沙屋苑「人工湖」塑膠建 業主抗議<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】湖南長沙一個新入伙的私人屋苑大量鋪設「植草磚」當綠化地，又以塑膠製作「人工湖」，與業主預期相差甚遠，引起抗議。開發商表示，屋苑小區未規劃人工湖，塑膠湖只是景觀；事件目前仍在協調中。<br />\n<br />\n上觀新聞引述湖南都市頻道報道，長沙北辰中央公園D區4棟住宅交樓後，業主鍾先生表示，屋苑內的塑膠「人工湖」很滑稽，而且內鋪「植草磚」的面積太大，不僅有礙觀瞻，還不安全、灰塵多。事件亦引起居民的抗議，當地派出所警員表示，11月16日至17日，警方曾到屋苑維護治安，稱業主如果要維權，可以向街道辦、社區合理反映訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發展商長沙世紀御景房地產人員18日稱，對政府報批報建及銷售宣傳都未有規劃或提過建設人工湖，塑膠湖只是景觀。</span><br />\n<br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾好呀唔會有蚊"},{"pid":"514629663fcbb0fc0021f9f0ec5e3abcefb03ab6","tid":1741512,"uid":199376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"輕功水上漂"},{"pid":"3035a16c54277c4d82f671752ddf988c856bc0e1","tid":1741512,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca59d7f2d2bee841025468161780e5dd0b0e16c","tid":1741512,"uid":101917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"冇水咪唔會浸親囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf632abc92bc111afa639cb1792d46d59856b8a","tid":1741512,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲去